post.description:
V2LoginWithOption
inside the data you must be passed client_type_id field
you must be give environment_id and project_id in body or
Environment-Id hearder and project-id in query parameters or
X-API-KEY in hearder
login strategy must be one of the following values
["EMAIL", "PHONE", "EMAIL_OTP", "PHONE_OTP", "LOGIN", "LOGIN_PWD", "GOOGLE_AUTH", "APPLE_AUTH", "PHONE_PWD", "EMAIL_PWD"]

V2Register
in data must be have type, type must be one of the following values
["google", "apple", "email", "phone"]
client_type_id and role_id must be in body parameters
you must be give environment_id and project_id in body or
Environment-Id hearder and project-id in query parameters or
X-API-KEY in hearder
SendCode type must be one of the following values ["EMAIL", "PHONE"]
